<H1>Welcome to <BR>
Teledyne Brown Engineering!</H1>
</center>

For more than 40 years, Teledyne Brown Engineering has provided 
systems engineering, systems integration, software development, 
and hardware fabrication services for the U.S. Department of Defense, 
NASA, and private companies around the world.  We are drawing on our 
strong engineering and scientific base to diversify and develop 
innovative, high-quality products for the commercial market.
<p>

